Subject: [PATCH 15/22] cleanup computed properies in native ui classess
 (#2469)

* cleanup computed properies in native ui classess

To make the EmberJS linter happy

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix yarn install error

Move off some weird dependency forks back to the original (archived) ones

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

---------

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>
Signed-off-by: Aditya <jaiswal.aditya.deelip@gmail.com>
